3a0d67932bc14e0fffa","tid":2426259,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"91c5693ef89fb11a883c79f6c3324a8b525e6f0f","tid":2426259,"uid":315760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"即係我想做誠哥<br />\n但係我剩係做到中產 咁都係鬱鬰不得志?<br />\n事實真係未如我理想喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b411d78f5ab360628237bfb3e742eccfee37477e","tid":2426259,"uid":66593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737cb288d28fa84e3dea933ec5d1736297669a7f","tid":2426259,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T19:54:48.000Z","msg":"主角起碼有夢想有能力，已經好過好多平平庸庸混混噩噩就過咗大半世嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dfe3981f08243961bbbe7086a0c20d5a804df1","tid":2426259,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700ec49fb609ee40c0a6918a5f1aa7a98570300e","tid":2426259,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>《靈魂奇遇記》 Soul</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLzKoShnfGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLzKoShnfGE%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=01eddf2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLzKoShnfGE%2F&h=f334af0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLzKoShnfGE/</a><br />\n電影已死，從來只是偽命題。當電影由黑白片，變成彩色電影，有人會急不及待出來宣告「電影已死」；電視的發明，「電影已死」；電腦動畫的出現，「電影已死」；串流平台的興起，「電影已死」。但是請細心想想每每說出「電影已死」的時候，總會有一部接一部的電影經典出現在影迷的眼前，精彩地呈現當代的精神。如果看到有心人開始在新平台做電影，有人就來不及出來趾高氣揚宣告「電影已死」，不如細心想想他究竟是「印度神童」？還是他仍在戀棧美好的過去，已經趕不上時代？<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2021/01/f0e3b7de4bf94c4c8500a0cb3a98a82f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2021%2F01%2Ff0e3b7de4bf94c4c8500a0cb3a98a82f.jpg&h=9217ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本的吉卜力工作室、迪士尼的PIXAR（彼思），都為電影動畫帶來全新定義。這次PIXAR繼《玩轉老朋友》、《玩轉極樂園》後，再創高峰帶來《靈魂奇遇記》，言簡意賅帶來一篇讚頌生命、擁抱熱情的詩篇，看來電影再一次又死不了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>屬於成人的卡通 每道微小成就人生美好</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/tumblr-282e188a5946e6c9c6c1e8808c3ccfee-28c709ba-540-1609925744.gif?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Ftumblr-282e188a5946e6c9c6c1e8808c3ccfee-28c709ba-540-1609925744.gif%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A&h=9928ed67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影由最開始就表明了這是一套由大人出發的電影，主角阿祖的夢想成為一位爵士樂手，可惜事與願違被迫與現實妥協，只好鬱鬰不得志的在一間學校當起音樂老師。有一天阿祖終於獲得演出的機會，卻失足意外昏迷。接著阿祖的靈魂來到投胎先修班，並遇見了多年無法找到生命中的「火花」去「投胎」的22號。<br />\n<br />\n電影一直在探討生命的火花，到底是什麼？人生的目標是甚麼，是不少人窮其一生都在思考的問題，笛卡兒說過：「我思故我在」。不過導演告訴我們「生命」就是我們生活的小事，成就生命的意義，就是這些小事讓你有「想活著」的動力。22號在電影中段經歷過阿祖的人生，手執樹上的落葉，彷彿頓悟出「一花一世界、一葉一如來」的境界，找到生命的熱情，明白生命的美好，最終才可以前往地球。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/anigif-1609923856.gif?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fanigif-1609923856.gif%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A&h=c0fdc158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《靈魂奇遇記》說的道理很簡單，擁抱熱情，讚頌生命的美好。但PIXAR這次高明在沒有用老掉牙的方式說教，生命中的美好，不一定是追求夢想，反而每道微小都也成就了人生的美好。電影尾段，阿祖送22號前往地球獲得新生，鏡頭由遠至近拍向地球，在眼前掠過一幕幕生命的小事，美味的披薩、阿祖母親的關愛、街頭的音樂，是首首不同的生之頌。特別在戲院重開後，可以在大銀幕上感受電影的感動，看得人眼濕濕。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，香港版配音找來鄭中基、王苑之配音，配得出色、親切、生鬼，各位也不妨支持一下廣東話版。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HNHI5hDLORs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHNHI5hDLORs&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=fc0560fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HNHI5hDLORs</a><br />\n各位啱睇不妨俾個like，得閒睇完戲會打下文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=4ae1c99b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=32f3ddac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"每道微小 RB<br />\n可以做主題曲"},{"pid":"274cb2e6fa227e46424e1610978261d21d8290fd","tid":2426259,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dfe3981f08243961bbbe7086a0c20d5a804df1","tid":2426259,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700ec49fb609ee40c0a6918a5f1aa7a98570300e","tid":2426259,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>《靈魂奇遇記》 Soul</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLzKoShnfGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLzKoShnfGE%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=01eddf2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/